query:
UPDATE albums SET
                artist = ?1,
                title = ?2,
                label = ?3,
                catalog_number = ?4,
                format = ?5,
                country = ?6,
                released_year = ?7,
                cover_image_url = ?8,
                resource_url = ?9,
                have_count = ?10,
                want_count = ?11,
                avg_rating = ?12,
                ratings_count = ?13,
                updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
            WHERE discogs_release_id = ?14
